Package lavaplayer

Class AudioProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • lavaplayer.AudioProvider
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    sx.blah.discord.handle.audio.IAudioProvider
    public class AudioProvider
extends java.lang.Object
implements sx.blah.discord.handle.audio.IAudioProvider
    This is a wrapper around AudioPlayer which makes it behave as an IAudioProvider for D4J. As D4J calls canProvide before every call to provide(), we pull the frame in canProvide() and use the frame we already pulled in provide().
